<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_593_r2l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> . Vns hat ewr <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> der hans kawrhals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l3"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . vvie Er von . ſeins weıbs wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l4">bey vns ʒu rehten hab . Als wir euch <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeins briefs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l5">ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> ſchıcken hyrinne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> . Nu iſt dıeſelb ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l6">vormals hıe berehtet woꝛden . doch vvie darümb vvenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l8">Er <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd mitvaſten 
<add><ab facs="#facs_593_r2l7">ſchierſt </ab></add> darümb her 
<del rend="strikethrough">k </del> gen <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l9">kümt / So ſol Er cʒu vnd von vns für vns vnd alle dy </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l10"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd bey vns für <expan>Allermenkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / drey tag geleyte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l11"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Vnd <expan>alſdan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></del> <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l12">mitburger von den . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒu den Er <expan>ʒuſpr<ex>echen</ex></expan> hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l13"><expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogens</expan> ſleunigs rehten helffen / ob vvir des von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l14">Jm ermant werden nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat reht <expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_593_r2l15">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan></del> Vnd <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſ<ex>amkeit</ex></expan> wol Jr weiſt Jn 
